        "created_at": "2018-09-30T19:35:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=2954963\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2015 Jules Desjourneys Pouilly-Loch\u00e9</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, M\u00e2connais, Pouilly-Loch\u00e9 (9/30/2018)</em>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Powerful and complex aromas, concentrated on the palate with ripe pear, peach, spices and creamy richness. Really interesting and quite special!</p>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
